item.title: A Conversation about A.I.D.S
item.description:
We discuss the AIDS virus and HIV and why it's still disproportionately still higher in the Black and Latino communities and what issues are driving those numbers. The homie Big Court from the Holdin Court podcast sits in with us on this important discussion
